$grp PS_MissionDescription : "{3136BE42592F3B1B}PrefabsEditable/MissionDescription/EditableMissionDescription.et" {
 SIT {
  coords 655.944 68.378 5220.233
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "<h2>PRELIMS</h2>"\
  "DTL: 23/07/2021, 0800hr, Ruha."\
  "Weather: Heavy overcast with moderate rain."\
  ""\
  "<h2>LORE</h2>"\
  "Over the past few days, experienced separatist fighters have taken control of a small hamlet along a key Alternative Supply Route (ASR) in the Ruha region. They have since fortified the area, establishing defensive positions and a checkpoint to dominate the road."\
  ""\
  "From this position, the separatists have been stopping and extorting civilian traffic while preventing Ruha Security Forces from moving reinforcements and supplies through the area. Their continued presence is disrupting movement across the region and strengthening their hold on the surrounding territory."\
  ""\
  "In response, a platoon from the Princess of Wales’s Royal Regiment, has been tasked with clearing the hamlet, restoring freedom of movement along the MSR, and removing the separatist threat from the area."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 CS {
  coords 655.944 68.378 5220.233
  m_sTitle "Comsig"
  m_sTextData "<h2>CALLSIGNS</h2>"\
  "• PLT Signaller - 32"\
  "• OC - 32A"\
  "• SGT - 32B"\
  "• 1SEC - 32C"\
  "• 2SEC - 32D"\
  "• 3SEC - 32E"\
  ""\
  "<h2>FREQ/CHAN</h2>"\
  "• Platoon net - 48hz"\
  "• HQ - 38.4hz"\
  "• 1SEC - 38.2hz"\
  "• 2SEC - 38.0hz"\
  "• 3SEC - 38.6hz"\
  ""\
  "<h2>PYROTECHNICS & SIGNALS</h2>"\
  "• White smoke - Concealment"\
  "• Blue smoke - Friendly location"\
  "• Red smoke - Enemy location"\
  "• Purple smoke - Spare"\
  ""\
  "<h2>PASSWORDS</h2>"\
  "All can be changed at CO's discretion."\
  "• <b>Challenge:</b> Chinese | <b>Password:</b> Chicken"\
  "• Running password: 1"\
  ""\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 EF {
  coords 655.944 68.378 5220.233
  m_sTitle "Enemy forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>"\
  "Enemy forces consist of an experienced, motorised separatist cell estimated at approximately 25 personnel in strength.  "\
  "They are currently dug in within a small hamlet located west of our position at GRID: 061081"\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>"\
  "• Partisan reports indicate the cell operates with 1× BRDM, attack drone capability, and several unarmed vehicles used for transport.  "\
  "• The enemy has had several days to prepare the area, establishing infantry fighting positions and vehicle cover in and around the hamlet.  "\
  "A fortified checkpoint has been constructed along the ASR, featuring a bunker and a static PKM oriented south down the road.  "\
  "All known enemy positions have been marked on the map."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 FF {
  coords 655.944 68.378 5220.233
  m_sTitle "Friendly forces"
  m_sTextData "<h2>COMPOSITION & DISPOSITION</h2>"\
  "We are light infantry from 3rd Platoon, B Company, 2nd Battalion, Princess of Wales’s Royal Regiment.  "\
  "The platoon consists of 32 personnel and is currently staged at the harbour area due east at GRID: 070077, ready to step off immediately."\
  ""\
  "<h2>STRENGTHS & CAPABILITIES</h2>"\
  "• Anti-tank team attached to us in HQ. "\
  "• Organic drone reconnaissance available at HQ level.  "\
  "• A counter-drone specialist equipped with a jammer effective up to 300 metres is attached to HQ."\
  "• Each section is equipped with 1× LAW66 L1A1 anti-tank launcher.  "\
  "• Everyone has optics."\
  ""\
  "<h2>SERVICE & SUPPORT</h2>"\
  "A supply crate is available at the staging location containing:  "\
  "• 1× MAVIC reconnaissance drone  "\
  "• 4× MAVIC batteries  "
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 MIS {
  coords 655.944 68.378 5220.233
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "<h2>MISSION STATEMENT</h2>"\
  "Our missision is to conduct a DELIBERATE ASSAULT to SECURE the hamlet in order to DISRUPT separatist operations along the ASR and restore freedom of movement through the area."\
  ""\
  "<h2>MISSION DESCRIPTION</h2>"\
  "Separatist forces have occupied and fortified a hamlet along an ASR. Using it as a checkpoint to control civilian traffic, extort locals, and block Ruha Security Forces from reinforcing further south."\
  ""\
  "3rd Platoon has been tasked with conducting a deliberate clearance of the hamlet. We are to advance from the east, neutralize all hostile forces, and secure the settlement to allow normal traffic and security movement to resume along the ASR."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "UK"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
}